data.description: Desirable Lakeview Home! Home boasts ample space & a serene location in the sought-after Lakeview school district. The home features 4 beds, 2.5 baths & over 2,000 sq. ft of living space, offering plenty of room to spread out. The home backs up to a charming small lake shared by only a few homes, providing a serene escape right in your backyard. Imagine peaceful mornings with coffee on the deck overlooking the water. Featuring an attached two car garage & a convenient circle drive for easy access, this home is designed for functionality. Inside, discover a spacious layout w/ a large bonus room ideally located facing the lake perfect for a playroom or office! This prime location is not only steps away from the water, but also within walking distance to Riverside Elementary Enjoy the best of both worlds- a peaceful retreat & excellent schools, all within easy reach. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of paradise! Call us today for a private showing 269-268-5454
